    "incident_name": "Warehouse pallet-manifest ETL hangs on a network call",
    "category": "Stuck/Hung Job",
    "severity": "Sev-2 (High)",
    "description": "Stuck/Hung Job incident on the Forecasting pipeline (RTL_FCT_STUCK): warehouse pallet-manifest ETL hangs on a network call.",
    "symptoms": "The MinIO-to-Snowflake COPY task for pallet manifests has been running 11 hours against a typical 25-minute duration, with no CPU activity in the container.",
    "root_cause": "A network ACL change on the MinIO side silently dropped outbound keep-alive packets, leaving the TCP connection in a half-open state that the client library never times out on.",
    "business_impact": "Warehouse manifest data unavailable, blocking put-away confirmation for two full inbound truck shipments.",
    "resolution": "Kill and restart the task with a client-side socket timeout configured; escalate the network ACL issue to infrastructure."
  },
